dc_title_s: Future Land Use Bayfield County, WI 2010
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents future land use for Bayfield County in 2010.
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated in fall of 2017 to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Download
